markdownRemark.html: Located to the north west of Isla Canela, this club has had nine holes in play for a number of years and in November 1996 opened the second nine. Natural lakes border a number of holes, and the greens are generally large and well-protected by bunkers. The Isla Canela golf course is suitable for all types of players and each hole presents a different challenge.
